Package: aicompetency-agent
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: systemd (>= 240)
Maintainer: Aptor <support@aptor.com>
Description: AI Competency Agent - Local Python execution agent
 AI Competency Agent provides a local WebSocket server for executing
 Python code in Jupyter kernels. It runs as a background service and
 automatically starts on system boot.
 .
 The agent exposes a WebSocket server on ws://127.0.0.1:8889 for
 browser-based notebook interfaces to connect and execute Python code
 locally on the user's machine.
 .
 Features:
  - Local Python code execution via Jupyter kernels
  - WebSocket API for browser integration
  - Automatic service management via systemd
  - File upload support
  - Kernel restart and interrupt capabilities
